name: YOUR ACTIONS DO NOT EFFECT THE ENDING
name_original: YOUR ACTIONS DO NOT EFFECT THE ENDING
description:
In YOUR ACTIONS DO NOT EFFECT THE ENDING, you play as a child, and interact with your family. Nothing you do can change how the story ends. What you can control is what you see. Can you put together the entire story?

YOUR ACTIONS DO NOT EFFECT THE ENDING deals with a family going through an unfortunate and possibly traumatic event. Content warnings include infidelity, parental arguments, and alcohol.
